org.ensembl.variation.driver
Interface LDFeatureAdaptor

All Superinterfaces:
Adaptor, FeatureAdaptor, java.rmi.Remote
public interface LDFeatureAdaptor
extends FeatureAdaptor

Provides database access for retrieving LDFeatures as either a simple List or wrapped in an optimised LDFeaturesContainer.

Craig Melsopp
